name: AVAssetReader.Status
desc: Values that represent the possible states of an asset reader.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: The asset reader is in an unknown state.

items.name: case reading
items.desc: The asset reader is successfully reading samples from its asset.

items.name: case completed
items.desc: The asset reader completes reading all samples within its specified time range.

items.name: case failed
items.desc: The asset reader can no longer read samples from its asset because of an error.

items.name: case cancelled
items.desc: The asset reader can no longer read samples because you canceled reading.
